A police officer was  shot at the corner of Winter Avenue and Musgrave Road, a short while ago. The officer is in a critical condition and was rushed to hospital for urgent medical care. The policeman  sustained a gunshot wound to his leg. One suspect has been arrested. Another  one suspect fled in a getaway vehicle alleged to have cloned plates.There is a contingent of SAPS members on scene as a manhunt is underway for the suspect at large. The circumstances surrounding the shooting are unclear at this stage but speculation is rife that the shooting was related to an attempted hijacking.